data.title: Warner Baxter
data.meta_description: All about Warner Baxter: biography, date of birth and age, place of birth, height, eye color
data.text:
Warner Baxter (Warner Leroy Baxter) - American actor (1889-1951). He was born March 29, 1889 in Columbus, United States of America.

Best known for his work on films such as In Old Arizona (1928), 42nd Street (1933), Fox Movietone Follies of 1934 (1934), Crooks in Clover (1933).
